<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPal9">
<l>ētamil taṇṇumai yekkam mattaḷi yāḻkuḻal muḻavamō ṭicaiticai keḻumik</l>
<l>kītaṅkaḷ pāṭiṉar kiṉṉarar keruṭarkaḷ kantaru varavar kaṅkulu ḷellām</l>
<l>mātavar vāṉavar cāraṇa riyakkar cittarum mayaṅkiṉar tiruvaṭi toḻuvāṉ</l>
<l>ātali lavarkkunā ḷōlakka maruḷa varaṅkattam māpaḷḷi yeḻuntaru ḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Throughout the night,</l>
<l>The kinnaras, the garuḍas, [and] those gandharvas sang songs,</l>
<l>playing music [that resounded all] the directions,</l>
<l>with faultless taṇṇumai-drums, [the stringed] ekkam¬s, mattaḷi-drums, lutes , flutes,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] muḻavu-drums;</l>
<l>The ascetics, celestials, Cāraṇas, Yakṣas and Siddhas</l>
<l>have become anxious to worship [Your] sacred feet.</l>
<l>Therefore, in order to bless them with a day audience,</l>
<l>O Lord of Raṅgam, do grace to wake up from sleep!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
